OL,3,CThe return of The Zutons, Liverpool
OL,4,Cband back on the road
OL,6,FGranada Reports correspondent Tim
OL,7,FScott talks to The Zutons about their
OL,8,Fnew music and the upcoming tour.
OL,10,FIt's sixteen years since the
OL,11,FMerseyside band released an album, now
OL,12,Ffans can look forward to a new one and
OL,13,Fa nationwide tour.
OL,15,FThe group, singer, songwriter, and
OL,16,Fguitarist Dave McCabe, drummer Sean
OL,17,FPayne, and saxophonist Abi Harding
OL,18,Frelease 'The Big Decider' on April
OL,19,F26th.
