OL,3,CThe return of The Zutons, Liverpool
OL,4,Cband back on the road
OL,6,FOn the same day they play the Olympia
OL,7,Fin their home city of Liverpool on a
OL,8,Ftour that starts on April 12th in
OL,9,FBristol. They play Manchester on 13th
OL,10,FApril at New Century Hall.
OL,12,FThe album was produced by the
OL,13,Flegendary Nile Rodgers, who founded
OL,14,Fthe soul and funk band Chic. He has
OL,15,Fworked with every major name in the
OL,16,Findustry including David Bowie,
OL,17,FMadonna and Duran Duran.
