OL,3,CThe return of The Zutons, Liverpool
OL,4,Cband back on the road
OL,6,FRodgers says 'They reached out to me,
OL,7,Fthey sent me some demos which I liked
OL,8,Fright away and I just can't help it, I
OL,9,Flove good music. And then I realised
OL,10,Fthat these were the guys who did
OL,11,FValerie and I was like, I'm into
OL,12,Fthis'. He refers to the smash hit Amy
OL,13,FWinehouse track, written and
OL,14,Foriginally performed by The Zutons.
OL,16,FThe band say they had such a good time
OL,17,Frecording the album they didn't want
OL,18,Fto leave the revered Abbey Road
OL,19,Fstudios in London.
