OL,3,CThe return of The Zutons, Liverpool
OL,4,Cband back on the road
OL,6,FDave McCabe has been candid about his
OL,7,Fyears of addiction to what he says was
OL,8,F'everything other than heroin and
OL,9,Fcrack'.
OL,11,F'It was a laugh for a good ten years,
OL,12,Fbut then the last six it wasn't and
OL,13,Fyou kinda, like, knew you had to stop.'
OL,15,FHe says his fiance and their son gave
OL,16,Fhim the reason to get clean, he
OL,17,Fstarted when his partner got pregnant.
OL,19,F"If that hadn't happened I'd probably
OL,20,Fstill be dipping in and out of it,' he
OL,21,Fsays.
