OL,3,CThe return of The Zutons, Liverpool
OL,4,Cband back on the road
OL,6,FAbi Harding agrees adding 'We probably
OL,7,Fwouldn't have been here doing this'.
OL,9,FBoth say time has flown and somehow
OL,10,Fgone slowly in parts in the last two
OL,11,Fdecades.
OL,13,FAsked if the chemistry in the band is
OL,14,Fthe same Abi says, 'It's better, I
OL,15,Fthink it's better than it was before'.
OL,17,FFor fans it looks like it's been well
OL,18,Fworth the wait.
